  "detailed_description": "<h1>Join Discord!</h1><p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153160/extras/3a3b783d417805b13a34323d37ad8f69.avif?t=1691786383\" width=600 height=150 /></span></h2></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153160/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1691786383\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153160/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1691786383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153160/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1691786383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Blind Sound</strong> is a first person psychological horror game, featuring a Terrifying Environment and a Rich Story.<br><br><strong>STORYLINE</strong><br>What would you do if you Stuck in a Facility with a lot of Creepy Creatures? Play as a Victim, and Try to Escape from this hell! You Shouldn't be here but now it's too late to leave, Make your Decisions. Maybe you can still escape and no matter what never trust them?<br><br><strong>Characters</strong><br>Every character in Blind Sound has a story that blends seamlessly into the main narrative. Watch every step you make and be careful not to attract any unwanted attention. You won’t be alone here.<br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br>Use your FlashLight to Escape, Find the weakness of the Creatures and Try to Survive in this Facility.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153160/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1691786383\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153160/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1691786383\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2153160/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1691786383\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><strong>Blind Sound</strong> is a first person psychological horror game, featuring a Terrifying Environment and a Rich Story.<br><br><strong>STORYLINE</strong><br>What would you do if you Stuck in a Facility with a lot of Creepy Creatures? Play as a Victim, and Try to Escape from this hell! You Shouldn't be here but now it's too late to leave, Make your Decisions. Maybe you can still escape and no matter what never trust them?<br><br><strong>Characters</strong><br>Every character in Blind Sound has a story that blends seamlessly into the main narrative. Watch every step you make and be careful not to attract any unwanted attention. You won’t be alone here.<br><br><strong>Gameplay</strong><br>Use your FlashLight to Escape, Find the weakness of the Creatures and Try to Survive in this Facility.",
